snippet.title: Live Coding: Bug Bounty Browser Extension (WIP)
snippet.description:
In a previous stream we looked at making web browser extensions. We began a bug bounty tool but didn't get too far. Tonight we will add more features to make it more useful.

GitHub: https://www.github.com/DevDungeon
Support the stream: https://streamlabs.com/devdungeon
Join Discord: https://discord.gg/JWsSHJC
Get $100 credit for signing up to Digital Ocean: https://m.do.co/c/5ccd98162d85
